WEBVTT

00:00:08.224 --> 00:00:12.162 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
At John 15:20, Jesus said:

00:00:12.162 --> 00:00:15.598 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
“A slave is not greater than his master.

00:00:15.598 --> 00:00:20.136 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If they have persecuted me,
they will also persecute you.”

00:00:21.104 --> 00:00:24.874 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How will we react when we are mistreated?

00:00:24.874 --> 00:00:28.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How will we find the strength to endure?

00:00:28.812 --> 00:00:33.149 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We have a record of faithful servants of old.

00:00:33.149 --> 00:00:38.021 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We know that Jehovah’s people can endure.

00:00:38.021 --> 00:00:40.323 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But we also have the record

00:00:40.323 --> 00:00:43.893 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of Jehovah’s Witnesses in modern times.

00:00:43.893 --> 00:00:46.830 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The following video draws on footage

00:00:46.830 --> 00:00:51.668 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from two previously released videos
by the organization.

00:00:51.668 --> 00:00:55.638 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It highlights two outstanding examples:

00:00:55.638 --> 00:00:59.209 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
our brothers in Germany during World War II

00:00:59.209 --> 00:01:02.245 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and our brothers in the former Soviet Union

00:01:02.245 --> 00:01:05.248 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the years that followed the war.

00:01:05.248 --> 00:01:07.951 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It also reveals the tactics

00:01:07.951 --> 00:01:11.387 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that enemies of the truth consistently use

00:01:11.387 --> 00:01:14.424 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—to no avail—against Jehovah’s people.

00:01:15.959 --> 00:01:19.162 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Reviewing and meditating on the examples

00:01:19.162 --> 00:01:21.831 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of these faithful brothers and sisters

00:01:21.831 --> 00:01:25.068 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
will prepare us for what lies ahead,

00:01:25.068 --> 00:01:29.739 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
will fill us with courage,
and will strengthen our faith.

00:01:33.409 --> 00:01:36.646 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
On January 30, 1933,

00:01:36.646 --> 00:01:38.848 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Adolf Hitler comes to power.

00:01:38.848 --> 00:01:41.985 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hitler gave the people jobs.

00:01:41.985 --> 00:01:44.521 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He restored their faith

00:01:44.521 --> 00:01:47.524 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the fatherland.

00:01:47.524 --> 00:01:51.327 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He is hailed as their savior.

00:01:51.327 --> 00:01:55.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But the Witnesses could not give to a man
what they believed belonged to God.

00:01:55.999 --> 00:01:58.234 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thus, a battle line

00:01:58.234 --> 00:02:02.071 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was drawn over a simple greeting
—“Heil Hitler.”

00:02:05.809 --> 00:02:08.778 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s Witnesses
refused to say “Heil Hitler”

00:02:08.778 --> 00:02:12.382 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because it meant
“Salvation comes from Hitler.”

00:02:13.917 --> 00:02:15.919 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At his job in a steel mill,

00:02:15.919 --> 00:02:18.922 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
one Witness faced this test.

00:02:18.922 --> 00:02:21.257 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was the only one among 2,000

00:02:21.257 --> 00:02:22.592 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
who did not raise my hand

00:02:22.592 --> 00:02:24.928 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
and did not return the German salute

00:02:24.928 --> 00:02:27.397 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—every day running the gauntlet,
since I was required

00:02:27.397 --> 00:02:29.532 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to give the German salute,
and I simply said,

00:02:29.532 --> 00:02:31.701 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Good day.”

00:02:31.701 --> 00:02:34.938 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Children were drawn into the battle.

00:02:34.938 --> 00:02:39.409 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Six-year-old Paul Gerhard Kusserow,

00:02:39.409 --> 00:02:41.444 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
like other Witness children, was pressured

00:02:41.444 --> 00:02:43.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by students and teachers.

00:02:43.780 --> 00:02:46.449 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As soon as I entered school,

00:02:46.449 --> 00:02:49.786 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the head teacher and the pupils confronted me

00:02:49.786 --> 00:02:52.288 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and tried to make me say, “Heil Hitler.”

00:02:54.524 --> 00:02:59.495 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
More than 800 children were taken away
from their Witness parents by the Gestapo.

00:02:59.495 --> 00:03:04.500 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In one German state after another,
the police shut down meetings

00:03:04.500 --> 00:03:07.637 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the Witnesses
and prohibit their door-to-door preaching.

00:03:10.273 --> 00:03:13.710 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
At first, there were nasty words,

00:03:13.710 --> 00:03:15.912 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
sometimes a beating,

00:03:15.912 --> 00:03:19.749 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but soon enough, it led to the first arrests.

00:03:24.988 --> 00:03:28.958 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Starting in 1937, Jehovah’s Witnesses
were given a purple triangle

00:03:28.958 --> 00:03:30.960 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as a sign.

00:03:32.862 --> 00:03:35.265 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s Witnesses

00:03:35.265 --> 00:03:36.332 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
were the only religious group

00:03:36.332 --> 00:03:39.168 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
that made up a separate category of inmates.

00:03:42.272 --> 00:03:46.776 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Jehovah’s Witnesses
received especially severe treatment.

00:03:49.112 --> 00:03:52.782 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The goal was to destroy this religious group;

00:03:52.782 --> 00:03:56.419 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
there were to be
no more Witnesses in Germany.

00:03:58.588 --> 00:04:03.293 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Nazis, obsessed with breaking
the Witnesses’ stubborn commitment,

00:04:03.293 --> 00:04:06.129 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
made them an extraordinary offer.

00:04:06.129 --> 00:04:08.131 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Each Witness could buy

00:04:08.131 --> 00:04:11.234 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
his freedom for a price: his signature 

00:04:11.234 --> 00:04:13.236 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and his faith.

00:04:13.236 --> 00:04:15.405 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Witnesses in prisons and camps

00:04:15.405 --> 00:04:17.941 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
were repeatedly handed
a piece of paper and a pen.

00:04:17.941 --> 00:04:21.477 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Very few signed.

00:04:21.477 --> 00:04:24.180 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
When I was to be released from prison,

00:04:24.180 --> 00:04:26.182 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
I was given a paper to sign.

00:04:26.182 --> 00:04:29.085 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
It required that I give up my faith

00:04:29.085 --> 00:04:32.689 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and recognize the German government
as the highest authority,

00:04:32.689 --> 00:04:35.158 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
place myself under the Hitler government,

00:04:35.158 --> 00:04:39.195 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and consider the Bible as a false doctrine.

00:04:39.195 --> 00:04:42.799 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I said, “That’s out of the question!”

00:04:44.834 --> 00:04:48.604 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The unity among the sisters and the brothers

00:04:48.604 --> 00:04:51.307 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
—that gave us so much strength.

00:04:51.307 --> 00:04:55.111 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was our aim
to endure under all circumstances.

00:04:55.111 --> 00:04:57.146 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We never prayed to be set free.

00:04:57.146 --> 00:04:59.148 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We prayed for strength to endure.

00:04:59.148 --> 00:05:01.150 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Everything else was unimportant.

00:05:01.150 --> 00:05:04.387 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What mattered
was standing up for Jehovah’s name.

00:05:24.273 --> 00:05:26.876 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
On February 19, 1951,

00:05:26.876 --> 00:05:31.381 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the head of the security police
presented a secret plan to Stalin.

00:05:31.381 --> 00:05:34.117 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
All of Jehovah’s Witnesses

00:05:34.117 --> 00:05:37.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—including infants and pregnant women—
would be exiled.

00:05:37.854 --> 00:05:41.290 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The plan was code-named “Operation North.”

00:05:41.290 --> 00:05:43.860 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Stalin approved it.

00:05:46.829 --> 00:05:50.400 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Interestingly, the Witnesses
were offered a way to avoid deportation.

00:05:51.434 --> 00:05:54.637 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The man in charge
of the deportation of our family

00:05:54.637 --> 00:05:57.173 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
tried to persuade Father to sign a paper

00:05:57.173 --> 00:05:58.775 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
renouncing the organization

00:05:58.775 --> 00:05:59.876 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:06:00.877 --> 00:06:03.713 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Few Witnesses, if any, accepted this offer.

00:06:05.148 --> 00:06:07.450 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Once in Siberia,
the Witnesses were dropped off

00:06:07.450 --> 00:06:09.318 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at settlements along the rail lines.

00:06:09.318 --> 00:06:12.055 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The majority of the Witnesses

00:06:12.055 --> 00:06:14.057 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
were forced to cut trees.

00:06:15.758 --> 00:06:17.393 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
We recalled the time when the Israelites

00:06:17.393 --> 00:06:18.594 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
lived in Egypt

00:06:18.594 --> 00:06:20.797 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
and how they were forced to work.

00:06:20.797 --> 00:06:24.367 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We prayed, “God,
make our faith stronger so that this work,

00:06:24.367 --> 00:06:27.503 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
which is beyond our strength,
will not shake us.”

00:06:28.638 --> 00:06:30.640 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Stalin’s death in 1953

00:06:30.640 --> 00:06:32.942 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
brought hope of relief.

00:06:32.942 --> 00:06:35.545 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But relief would be a long time

00:06:35.545 --> 00:06:37.346 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in coming.

00:06:37.346 --> 00:06:39.849 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The new regime went on in the same course.

00:06:39.849 --> 00:06:41.851 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
They arrested and sentenced us.

00:06:43.119 --> 00:06:47.690 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Most arrested Witnesses
were sentenced to labor camps.

00:06:47.690 --> 00:06:51.661 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In court, they could not expect a fair trial.

00:06:51.661 --> 00:06:55.698 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Guilty verdicts
had already been decided upon.

00:06:55.698 --> 00:06:58.468 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Under the Khrushchev administration,

00:06:58.468 --> 00:07:01.137 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
special “reeducation” camps were set up,

00:07:01.137 --> 00:07:03.706 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
designed to turn inmates from their beliefs.

00:07:05.041 --> 00:07:09.278 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
During this period, propaganda films
designed to discredit Jehovah’s Witnesses

00:07:09.278 --> 00:07:13.549 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
were distributed throughout the USSR.

00:07:21.657 --> 00:07:24.427 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Whoever has studied persecution in the past

00:07:24.427 --> 00:07:26.662 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
has seen that in one way or another,

00:07:26.662 --> 00:07:29.465 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
persecution is always built on a lie.

00:07:29.465 --> 00:07:31.834 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The victim is slandered.

00:07:33.236 --> 00:07:35.805 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Besides using propaganda, for many years,

00:07:35.805 --> 00:07:40.610 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the KGB recruited informers
to infiltrate Witness congregations.

00:07:40.610 --> 00:07:44.514 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For instance, in 1968,
the KGB district director

00:07:44.514 --> 00:07:47.150 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
offered Nikolai Bychkov an assignment.

00:07:47.150 --> 00:07:49.118 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
He requested me

00:07:49.118 --> 00:07:51.954 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
to spy on Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:07:51.954 --> 00:07:56.592 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One Witness booklet that compared
the teaching of evolution with the Bible

00:07:56.592 --> 00:07:59.262 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
changed the KGB informer’s viewpoint.

00:07:59.262 --> 00:08:03.232 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No one could answer that question:

00:08:03.232 --> 00:08:05.168 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
how life appeared.

00:08:05.168 --> 00:08:07.537 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the Bible,

00:08:07.537 --> 00:08:11.307 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I could find answers to those questions.

00:08:11.307 --> 00:08:14.877 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In Khabarovsk in 1984, Nikolai Bychkov,

00:08:14.877 --> 00:08:18.781 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
now a baptized Witness,
and several fellow believers

00:08:18.781 --> 00:08:20.783 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
were accused of anti-Soviet activities.

00:08:22.318 --> 00:08:25.421 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But the all-out attack
on the Witnesses’ faith backfired

00:08:25.421 --> 00:08:27.423 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on the persecutors.

00:08:28.357 --> 00:08:31.194 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In Germany and in Soviet times,

00:08:31.194 --> 00:08:32.895 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
they thought that you could get rid

00:08:32.895 --> 00:08:35.097 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
of an idea by using extreme violence.

00:08:35.865 --> 00:08:38.601 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But it turned out
that when an idea is strong,

00:08:38.601 --> 00:08:40.603 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it makes people strong.

00:08:40.603 --> 00:08:43.973 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So the outcome was just the opposite
of what was expected.

00:08:45.741 --> 00:08:48.578 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In March 1991,

00:08:48.578 --> 00:08:51.314 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s Witnesses
were legally registered in Russia.

00:08:53.649 --> 00:08:55.351 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
I think it is frightening

00:08:55.351 --> 00:08:58.688 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
only if you’ve never faced difficulties.

00:08:58.688 --> 00:09:03.693 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But once you face them,
you know that special strength.

00:09:03.693 --> 00:09:06.262 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When we rely on Jehovah

00:09:06.262 --> 00:09:09.665 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—we ask for his guidance;
we ask for his help—

00:09:09.665 --> 00:09:12.068 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we will always get it.

00:09:33.923 --> 00:09:37.326 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In addition to horrible physical treatment,

00:09:37.326 --> 00:09:40.096 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God’s people faced slander,

00:09:40.096 --> 00:09:43.633 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
outright lies, and fabrications,

00:09:43.633 --> 00:09:47.336 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even in the form of propaganda films.

00:09:47.336 --> 00:09:52.341 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Opposers attempted to infiltrate
our brotherhood with informants.

00:09:52.341 --> 00:09:57.346 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But as we saw
in the example of Nikolai Bychkov,

00:09:57.346 --> 00:10:00.449 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
such devious plans are in vain

00:10:00.449 --> 00:10:04.420 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when pitted against the truth
from God’s Word.

00:10:04.420 --> 00:10:08.357 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As Professor Nikolai Gordienko noted,

00:10:08.357 --> 00:10:13.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“When an idea is strong,
it makes people strong.”

00:10:13.229 --> 00:10:15.698 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What idea can be stronger

00:10:15.698 --> 00:10:19.302 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
than the reality of our Father, Jehovah;

00:10:19.302 --> 00:10:21.837 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
his reigning King, Jesus Christ;

00:10:21.837 --> 00:10:26.842 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and his Kingdom,
now poised to thwart all opposition?

00:10:26.842 --> 00:10:31.280 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And so, what people
can possibly be stronger

00:10:31.280 --> 00:10:33.482 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
than Jehovah’s people?

00:10:33.482 --> 00:10:37.953 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As our brothers in Russia
and other areas of the earth

00:10:37.953 --> 00:10:40.389 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
face renewed opposition

00:10:40.389 --> 00:10:44.827 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and as we all face the prospect
of being mistreated

00:10:44.827 --> 00:10:47.630 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
just as our Master, Jesus, was,

00:10:47.630 --> 00:10:50.533 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we are determined to stand firm

00:10:50.533 --> 00:10:55.071 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and remain faithful
no matter what the enemies of truth attempt.

